Between 17th-22th November 2014 Mr. Robert Porter and Mr. Syarif Abadi, experts from Tilburg University’s Institute for Interdisciplinary Studies of Civil Law and Conflict Resolution, based in the Netherlands,In this light the experts interviewed ADR communities, local authorities, and beneficiaries at Kratie and Kompong Cham who requested ADHOC’s ADR services in the past.
ADHOC’s ADR program is currently in its second year of implementation, Financial support is provided by the European Union, ADHOC so far provided ADR training in 9 provinces, including Kompot, Kompong Speu, Kompong Chhang, Battanbong, Bantey Meanchey, Kompong Thom, Kompong Cham, Kratie and Kandal.